Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.77,0:01:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so crowded!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.77,0:01:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it felt like a festival!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.77,0:01:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you go to Odaiba with your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.89,0:01:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but Himuro-kun kept bugging me to go to a hotel with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.26,0:01:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.03,0:01:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.10,0:01:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So did you go?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.90,0:01:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.63,0:01:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.32,0:01:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave them be!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.93,0:01:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff like that's nothing new to their relationship, you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.82,0:01:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Still…
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.68,0:02:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure you're in trouble.
