Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.43,0:02:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw her boyfriend holding hands with someone he used to love!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.19,0:02:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't come to the meeting spot,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.13,0:02:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't pick up her phone,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.84,0:02:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and wouldn't answer texts either.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.13,0:02:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus, what the hell is she doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.25,0:02:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I even getting a signal?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.82,0:02:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she did call me a while ago!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be asking {\i1}you{\i0} that!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.67,0:02:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are {\i1}you{\i0} doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.87,0:02:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just sit there waiting for texts like a loser!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.16,0:02:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,go visit Eba's home!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.52,0:03:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be tough to get out through the front doors since the teacher's keeping watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.80,0:03:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about using the emergency exit?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.45,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,From there and through the parking lot, you should be able to get outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.42,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll distract the teacher just to be safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.88,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! We've got a perfect plan!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,going to help me?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.72,0:03:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, and if we're gonna do it, we'll give it our all.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.75,0:03:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So buy me a drink!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice cream for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.38,0:03:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's gotta be Häagen Dazs green tea ice cream!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.70,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got until 10, when the teacher will be coming around for lights-out.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.15,0:03:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go find her and make up by then!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.34,0:03:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going back like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.18,0:03:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how angry she is,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.62,0:03:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,even if she hates me now,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.42,0:04:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see her.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see her.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see her!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.02,0:04:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Haruto and Yuzuki-chan met up by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they did!
