Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:41.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(-117.82,216.26)\blur0.5\fay-0.06\bord0\fs30\b0\c&H160D08&}Eba{\b1}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so stupid.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell am I doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.81,0:04:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You scared me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.82,0:05:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q3}I was wondering who the creepy guy loitering outside my house could be.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.21,0:05:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here for a school trip.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you call Eba for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to bring my phone.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.35,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I passed by her on my way back home.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.39,0:05:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how would I know?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.44,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never figure out what she's thinking anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.33,0:05:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she got a boyfriend and went to see him!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.56,0:05:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Long-distance relationships just don't last.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in her!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. I'm not stopping you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.41,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Please, can you call Eba for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.88,0:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably just wandering around.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave her, and she'll be back eventually.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind if she never came back, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.56,0:06:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what she's always like.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.65,0:06:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Winning people over by acting like she can't do anything by herself.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just hungry for attention.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.61,0:06:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, she's irritating to watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not like tha—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.18,0:06:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the same, Haruto-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.10,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're irritating to watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.77,0:06:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to stand there?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I might call the police
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.75,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and tell them I've got a stalker!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The night in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.23,0:07:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is so bright,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.61,0:07:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,yet I can't even find her.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.87,0:07:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.02,0:07:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anyone say that the meeting place changed?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.27,0:07:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably just wandering around.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.93,0:07:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave her, and she'll be back eventually.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.82,0:08:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind if she never came back, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.88,0:08:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Eba Yuzuki, and I'm from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.61,0:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.88,0:08:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents must be worried over letting you attend a high school this deep in the country.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.07,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but they let me since this is my dad's hometown,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd be staying at an acquaintance's house.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.09,0:08:28.40,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But really, you're such a beautiful young lady!{background}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.93,0:08:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When Eba came to Hiroshima, she was looking for a place to belong.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.83,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you for the compliment.{background}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.68,0:08:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything without you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.91,0:08:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I completely failed to notice that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting on.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.96,0:08:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me back with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.20,0:08:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just trying not to give in.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.09,0:09:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I drove her out.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.59,0:09:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think of her as my big sister.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.70,0:09:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just enduring it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.49,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Eba, where are you right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right behind you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just forcing a smile.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.47,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad got remarried.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.18,0:09:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My stepmother brought Rin-chan and Onii-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.69,0:09:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,relationships are a little awkward in my family.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we family?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.28,0:10:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't I like your family too?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.79,0:10:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's okay to cry if you're having a hard time.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.51,0:10:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll do anything to help.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.93,0:10:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be her place to belong.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.43,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to be a steady, reliable man whom she can trust.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.99,0:10:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Late!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.98,0:11:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.45,0:11:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent you a text saying that I'd come meet you,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.01,0:11:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but you forgot to take your phone.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.64,0:11:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I even checked hotels. I looked for you everywhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.22,0:11:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I did hear about what you and Nanami-chan were doing,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.61,0:11:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but after seeing something like that, no one would—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.14,0:12:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so, so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.66,0:12:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.44,0:12:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad we could meet!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.38,0:12:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to leave if you didn't show up in the next five minutes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.65,0:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.06,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, like...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.50,0:12:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.71,0:12:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that I'd never make you feel alone,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.80,0:12:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but then I went and did something like that,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.31,0:12:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm really, um...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.40,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.60,0:12:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're wasting time!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.68,0:13:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk about something other than apologies.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Eba.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.90,0:13:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just dumb, slow-witted, and shy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They're beautiful!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.84,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you want to come to this town?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.53,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.28,0:13:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea had to come from somewhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.33,0:13:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You came all the way here from Tokyo for school.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.84,0:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, I visited this town once. {once visisted this town.}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.96,0:14:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I really liked this place then.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the reason?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's strange!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.84,0:14:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's just—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.17,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say that was the reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.09,0:14:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just dumb, slow-witted, and shy.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.38,0:14:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't really bring myself to hold your hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.35,0:14:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the moment we met, I must have been...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.37,0:14:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...in love with you,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.94,0:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,probably since the moment we met,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,all this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.22,0:15:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in love with you for a whole lot longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, this!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari, that way!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, Takashi, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.92,0:15:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.00,0:15:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tell you! {Hnnnnnnng this is so cute}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.02,0:15:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go back!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.83,0:15:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.09,0:15:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to come here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.89,0:16:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, don't cry!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.90,0:16:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to a nice place, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A nice place?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is that nice place?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.11,0:16:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.52,0:16:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A flower blooms on this pond only once each year.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.91,0:16:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any flowers.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.71,0:16:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See it blooming on the pond?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.81,0:17:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a huge flower!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.85,0:17:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally smiled.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.71,0:17:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like this town now?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.42,0:17:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then no more crying.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.85,0:17:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because something bad happened,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.22,0:17:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but I feel all right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.65,0:17:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.28,0:17:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then come back again if something happens!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.65,0:17:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.65,0:17:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.07,0:17:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.51,0:18:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.28,0:18:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in place of a birthday gift.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I got something too...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.35,0:18:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't bring it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.21,0:18:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.58,0:18:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But as a boyfriend, I feel pathetic to be on the receiving end of things.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.46,0:18:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for me to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.89,0:18:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go back to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.04,0:18:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go back to Tokyo... and stay with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.13,0:18:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Feelings change.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.65,0:18:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.72,0:19:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But yours changed, didn't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.72,0:19:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q3}You loved Nanami-chan so much until a little while ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.63,0:19:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Feelings can change just like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.65,0:19:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Long-distance relationships never work out.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.56,0:19:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it won't be a long-distance relationship!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.26,0:19:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel that insecure,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.97,0:19:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to Tokyo with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.87,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that won't happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.98,0:19:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you do, I'll be troubled.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.11,0:20:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was really happy...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.37,0:20:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,when you asked me to be your girlfriend and said that you'd even go to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be with you for a while longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't nearly enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.12,0:21:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q3}We have to say goodbye here. Send my regards to your friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.30,0:21:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.53,0:21:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The more exciting it was to meet,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.50,0:21:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the sadder it feels to say goodbye, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.38,0:21:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.59,0:21:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.18,0:21:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking it's painful...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to be in a long-distance relationship.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.98,0:21:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then should we break up?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.77,0:21:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.81,0:21:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Haruto-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.42,0:21:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.38,0:22:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.76,0:22:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come see you again.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.82,0:22:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.75,0:22:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.33,0:22:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the one! The omelet rice from this restaurant called Amami was really good!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.81,0:22:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks delicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.39,0:22:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The waitresses were super cute too!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.98,0:22:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see them again.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:50.34,0:22:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can go to Tokyo alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.85,0:22:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:54.04,0:22:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come too, right, Haruto?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.35,0:22:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I'll go too.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.85,0:23:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You weren't even listening, were you?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.66,0:23:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was listening!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.48,0:23:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Nanami-chan, tell him something too!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.30,0:23:10.99,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, I don't really...{background}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.30,0:23:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be living away from each other for a while,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.99,0:23:12.60,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Haruto's always like this!{background}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.99,0:23:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure we'll be all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.60,0:23:14.74,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I bet Yuzuki-chan is all that's on his mind!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.75,0:23:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Our relationship transcends time and distance
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.25,0:23:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because our minds are connected.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.86,0:23:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Our long-distance love relationship...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.14,0:23:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,has only just begun.
