Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.41,0:23:51.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}aitai to omou sonna kimochi wa
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.41,0:23:51.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}Our longing to meet each other
Dialogue: 1,0:23:51.94,0:23:58.98,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}sora wo oyoideru kumo mitai ni
Dialogue: 1,0:23:51.94,0:23:58.98,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}Are like clouds drifting in the skies
Dialogue: 1,0:23:58.98,0:24:05.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}butsukatte tokete kieta
Dialogue: 1,0:23:58.98,0:24:05.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}They bump into each other and melt away
Dialogue: 1,0:24:06.65,0:24:13.85,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}itsukara darou surechigatteru
Dialogue: 1,0:24:06.65,0:24:13.85,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}We've always been just passing by each other
Dialogue: 1,0:24:13.85,0:24:17.48,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}sore demo dokoka de
Dialogue: 1,0:24:13.85,0:24:17.48,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}Even still, I'm here
Dialogue: 1,0:24:17.48,0:24:24.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}anata dake motometeiru
Dialogue: 1,0:24:17.48,0:24:24.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}Only looking for you
Dialogue: 1,0:24:24.90,0:24:28.59,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}aitakute sora ni egaita
Dialogue: 1,0:24:24.90,0:24:28.59,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}Wanting to meet you, I drew in the skies
Dialogue: 1,0:24:28.59,0:24:32.29,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}mirai eto tsuzuku negai
Dialogue: 1,0:24:28.59,0:24:32.29,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}A wish that carries on into the future
Dialogue: 1,0:24:32.29,0:24:35.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}kyou mo mata konna ni mo
Dialogue: 1,0:24:32.29,0:24:35.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}Even today, you're still
Dialogue: 1,0:24:35.81,0:24:38.67,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}mabushikute itoshikute
Dialogue: 1,0:24:35.81,0:24:38.67,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}So bright and lovely
Dialogue: 1,0:24:38.67,0:24:46.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}hidamari ni narande saiteru himawari mitai ni
Dialogue: 1,0:24:38.67,0:24:46.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}Like the sunflowers that bloom toward the glowing sun
Dialogue: 1,0:24:46.41,0:24:53.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}mitsumetetai kira kira my love
Dialogue: 1,0:24:46.41,0:24:53.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}I want to see you, my shiny love
